name: Oktoberfest
description:
Our Oktoberfest is a crystal clear, copper colored lager which features the rich and toasty flavors of both Munich and Vienna malts.  Lagering this beer accentuates these malt flavors, resulting in the most enjoyable fest bier!

Malts: Pilsner, Munich, Vienna, Cara-Vienna, Caramel 60
Hops: Liberty, Ultra
